  "translations": {
    "en": "He singled Himself out with Lordship and specified Himself with Oneness, and acquired glory and laudation for Himself alone, and was unique in tawhid and majesty and sublimity, and singled Himself out in praise, and was glorified through glorification. He is exalted above taking sons, and pure and sanctified beyond contact with women, and mighty and majestic beyond proximity to associates.",
